4:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f42096b1ea289d84a10df7967f7444a898edd069","tid":1631884,"uid":153258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:43:53.000Z","msg":"希望大家有個透切既明白<br />\n<br />\nBlack bloc 就係為左互相掩護<br />\n<br />\n而互相掩護 就係大家都要一同承擔被捕既風險<br />\n唔係著件黑衫而示支持 而係包到全身黑增加認人既難度 <br />\n<br />\n俾狗逗 冇錯 好多人都會驚 好正常<br />\n但出得黎既人有邊個係唔驚？<br />\n<br />\n手足係前線 係鏡頭前真係好似勇者無懼 但鏡頭後 散水之後 其實驚到仆街 驚俾人跟蹤驚隔離係鬼驚冇路走 <br />\n<br />\n恐懼是原始的情感 是無可避免 亦是源於無知 <br />\n即係話 你係可以控制你有幾驚<br />\n<br />\n出門前 <br />\n做足功課 理解敵我權益權限法律程序 <br />\n哩啲由第一日已經咁講 有幾多人真係有做？"},{"pid":"f551eed675ebb1d9c708567583efd011b2b91093","tid":1631884,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">8</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">提款日</span></span></strong><br />\n各大銀行總行撳錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634001/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">9</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">文宣日</span></span></strong><br />\n齊齊修補連儂牆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10月<span style=\"color: teal;\">10</span>日：<span style=\"color: orange;\">消費日</span></span></strong><br />\n全民幫襯黃色店鋪，18區排長龍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1634353/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"1f5456b7adb524223d784325b4b613cf99a346a2","tid":1631884,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:45:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"055c02ee1e25637968901c5d496dd6e90babe33c","tid":1631884,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:47:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0e1c7e96093bba2929e960eff0cb2b1232b0247","tid":1631884,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-